  ('heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-moex-00456', 'heelevel3-d0d1b9a2', 'heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-moex-111-f6c431ec', 'sub-heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據中位數投票者理論，如果一個國家的所得分配更為右偏時，則選民投票決定執行所得重分配 政策之公共支出：', '["會減少", "會增加", "會先增加再減少", "會先減少再增加"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:32:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "44c10a6685c9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b3991257716c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "324", "s": "0903", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "財政學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-moex-00457', 'heelevel3-d0d1b9a2', 'heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-moex-111-f6c431ec', 'sub-heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何項敘述乃屬規範經濟學所探討之議題？', '["對菸酒課稅，菸酒的價格可能提高", "對菸酒課稅，菸酒的需求量可能減少", "對菸酒課稅，低所得對菸酒的消費比重可能增加", "對菸酒課稅，是否有助所得分配更公平"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:32:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "44c10a6685c9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b3991257716c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "324", "s": "0903", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "財政學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-moex-00458', 'heelevel3-d0d1b9a2', 'heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-moex-111-f6c431ec', 'sub-heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '公共支出計畫於首年初投入一次性成本 50 億，次年初開始產生利益 3 億元直到永遠。其他條件 不變，若社會折現率為5%，此計畫的淨現值是：', '["0", "10億", "50億", "100億"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:32:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "44c10a6685c9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b3991257716c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "324", "s": "0903", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "財政學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-moex-00459', 'heelevel3-d0d1b9a2', 'heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-moex-111-f6c431ec', 'sub-heelevel3-d0d1b9a2-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '福利經濟學第二定理主要在闡述下列何種經濟概念？', '["所有消費者的邊際替代率均會相等", "所有生產者的邊際技術替代率均會相等", "完全競爭市場將會引導資源的配置效率", "可在不損及經濟效率下，達成分配的公平"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:32:01+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "44c10a6685c9", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b3991257716c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "324", "s": "0903", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "財政學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
